13:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"GPA kalkulyatori o'zbek 5-balli tizim baholarini xorijiy universitetlarning aksariyatida qo'llaniladigan xalqaro GPA shkalasiga (0-4.0) o'giradi. Moslik: «a'lo» (5) = 4.0; «yaxshi» (4) = 3.0; «qoniqarli» (3) = 2.0; «qoniqarsiz» (2) = 0. Xorijga o'qishga kirishni yoki «El-yurt umidi» dasturida ishtirok etishni rejalashtirgan O'zbekiston talabalari uchun aniq GPA hisobi juda muhim."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"GPA har bir fanning kreditlari (ECTS yoki akademik soatlari) ni hisobga olgan holda baholarning o'rtacha tortilgan qiymati sifatida hisoblanadi: GPA = Σ(GPA bahoxi × Kreditlar) / Σ(Kreditlar). Misol: 5 fan — «Matematika» (5/3 kr.) + «Fizika» (4/4 kr.) + «Ingliz tili» (5/2 kr.) + «Tarix» (4/2 kr.) + «Kimyo» (3/3 kr.) = (4,0×3 + 3,0×4 + 4,0×2 + 3,0×2 + 2,0×3) / 14 = 44/14 = 3,14."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Xorijiy universitetlarning O'zbekiston bitiruvchilaridan GPA talablari: AQSh (Ivy League) — 3.7 dan; Buyuk Britaniya (Russell Group) — 3.5 dan; Germaniya — 3.0 dan; Janubiy Koreya (KAIST, SNU) — 3.2 dan; Turkiya — 2.5 dan; Rossiya (MGU, VShE) — 3.0 dan. «El-yurt umidi» dasturi — magistratura uchun 3.5 GPA dan, bakalavr uchun 3.0 dan."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekistonning ba'zi OTMlari (Westminster, INHA, MDIS) allaqachon 100 balli tizimni qo'llaydi: 86-100 = A (4.0), 71-85 = B (3.0), 56-70 = C (2.0), 55 dan past = F (0). Kalkulyator ikkala baholash tizimini ham qo'llab-quvvatlaydi. Xorijga hujjat topshirishda GPA verifikatsiyasi uchun WES (World Education Services) bahosini ham taqdim etish tavsiya etiladi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Saytimizdagi GPA kalkulyatori: har bir fanning nomini, bahosini va kreditlar sonini kiriting — ikki xonali aniqlikda umumiy GPAni olasiz. Shuningdek, qaysi fanlar GPAni pastga tortayotgani va qayta topshirishda GPA necha punktga yaxshilanishi ko'rsatiladi. Xorijda magistraturaga tayyorlanayotgan talabalar uchun foydali."}]]}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Ko'p beriladigan savollar"}],["$","$L17",null,{"className":"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card px-4","children":[["$","$L18","0",{"value":"faq-0","children":[["$","$L19",null,{"className":"text-left text-foreground","children":"Baholarni GPAga qanday o'girish mumkin?"}],["$","$L1a",null,{"children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-muted-foreground","children":"5 = 4.0, 4 = 3.0, 3 = 2.0, 2 = 0. Har bir fanning kreditlarini hisobga olgan holda o'rtacha tortilgan qiymatni hisoblang."}]}]]}],"$L1b","$L1c","$L1d","$L1e"]}]]}],"$L1f"]}]
